{
  "info": {
    "name": "Patient Management System — Full API",
    "description": "Complete REST API collection for the Patient Management System. All endpoints route through the API Gateway at localhost:4004. Authentication is handled via JWT — use the Login request to get a token, which is automatically injected into all subsequent requests.\n\nCharacters used in test data:\n  👑 Chamuditha — SUPER_ADMIN (seeded)\n  👤 Sanduni   — ADMIN\n  🏥 Kasuni    — STAFF (receptionist)\n  🩺 Dr. Lakmal & Dr. Nethmi — DOCTORs\n  👩‍🦰 Tharushi  — PATIENT\n\nBase URL: {{base_url}}",
